|ID|OPERATOR           |NAME           |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
--------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |SELECT INTO        |               |3       |3           |
|1 |└─SUBPLAN SCAN     |ANONYMOUS_VIEW1|3       |3           |
|2 |  └─TABLE FULL SCAN|t1_            |3       |3           |
==============================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
