|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR               |:EX10001       |3       |2           |
|2 |  └─SELECT INTO                    |               |3       |2           |
|3 |    └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR            |               |3       |2           |
|4 |      └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (RANDOM)|:EX10000       |3       |1           |
|5 |        └─SUBPLAN SCAN             |ANONYMOUS_VIEW1|3       |1           |
|6 |          └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR      |               |3       |1           |
|7 |            └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |t1_            |3       |1           |
==============================================================================
